    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "REFERENCE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Telephone message CI Division Hq. OSI, 9 May 1952",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "SYNOPSIS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Investigation requested by Hq. OSI predicated on information received from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Air Technical Intelligence Center, Wright Patterson AFB that DONALD STEWART",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "and (FNU) TYLER had observed unconventional type aircraft on 29 March 1952",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "in the vicinity of Baltimore, Maryland. Information relayed to Air Technical",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Intelligence Center, Wright Patterson AFB by ULIUS LOUIS AMOSS who received",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "it from LOU CORBIN, a news commentator, employed by station WFBR, Baltimore,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Md. CORBIN interviewed, furnished information that DONALD STEWART, [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "and GEORGE TYLER III, [REDACTED] had been",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "interviewed by him on 24 and 27 April 1952 and had reported sighting a disc-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "like aircraft at approximately 2045 hours, 29 March 1952 on Ritchie Highway",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "near the intersection of US Route 301; that automobile engine stopped and paint",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "cracked as aircraft hovered 200 feet above car. STEWART interviewed and re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "lated substantially the same story which he had given CORBIN previously. FAY",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "FOI, Engineer, Westinghouse Electric Corporation, Baltimore, Md, interviewed,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "advised he had made complete examination of STEWART's vehicle at request of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "CORBIN; including examination with geiger counter and determined no unusual",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "defects. AMOSS interviewed, stated he had no direct knowledge of incident and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "had merely relayed information furnished him by CORBIN; advised that several",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "residents, Gibson Island, Maryland had heard unusual noises but none had observed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "any such aircraft. TYLER interviewed and confirmed statement given by STEWART",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "however, upon reinterview, admitted that he had not been with STEWART at the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "time of the alleged sighting, and had not seen any such aircraft; advised",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "that STEWART had asked him to tell that story and that he had done so. Inter-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "views conducted along Ritchie Highway in vicinity of location where aircraft",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
